OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning but the cloud
OL,6,Fgradually dissipating with sunny
OL,7,Fspells for most places by the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Low cloud likely lingering
OL,9,Falong the coast throughout the day.
OL,10,FFeeling warm in the sunshine, cooler
OL,11,Falong the coast with an onshore breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA clear evening for most.
OL,14,FOvernight, low cloud spreads inland
OL,15,Ffrom the North Sea, affecting many
OL,16,Fareas. Staying largely dry, with a
OL,17,Fgentle northeasterly wind, breezier
OL,18,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
