OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy morning gives way
OL,6,Fto a sunny afternoon. Breezy,
OL,7,Fespecially along the coast.
OL,8,FTemperatures remain above average,
OL,9,Fthough feeling cooler by the sea.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FGenerally cloudy mornings with sunny
OL,13,Fspells developing by the afternoons.
OL,14,FRemaining largely dry throughout.
OL,15,FBreezy at times, especially along the
OL,16,Fcoast. Feeling warm by day with
OL,17,Ftemperatures remaining above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
